'''.bit'''是当今[[互联网|互联网]]上[[域名系统|域名系统]]中的一个不常用的[[顶级域名|顶级域名]]，且不被[[ICANN|ICANN]]所承认。.bit域名是以[[Namecoin|Namecoin]]为基础的一个[[权力分散|分散式]]的域名系统。<ref name="desk1">{{Cite news | url=http://www.coindesk.com/what-are-namecoins-and-bit-domains/ | title=What are Namecoins and .bit domains? | work=CoinDesk | date=2013-06-18 | first=David | last=Gilson | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Hp73ED3F?url=http://www.coindesk.com/what-are-namecoins-and-bit-domains/ | archivedate=2013-07-03 | deadurl=yes | accessdate=2015-05-26 }}</ref>要使用.bit域名，-{zh-cn:用户;zh-tw:使用者}-需要Namecoin[[区块链|区块链]]、支持该域名的DNS服务器，或者是浏览器插件。

2014年2月，一个包含 Windows / Linux 的测试版的Firefox插件freespeechme被发布，它允许自动解析地址、分析Namecoin区块链以及在后台运行。<ref>{{Cite news | url=http://bitcoinmagazine.com/10190/freespeechme-new-anti-censorship-secure-domain-resolving-namecoin-based-plug/ | work=Bitcoin Magazine | title=FreeSpeechMe: The new anti-censorship and secure domain resolving Namecoin-based plug-in | first=Ferdinand | last=Reyes | date=2014-02-13 | accessdate=2015-05-26 | archive-date=2014-03-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140307044001/http://bitcoinmagazine.com/10190/freespeechme-new-anti-censorship-secure-domain-resolving-namecoin-based-plug/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>此外，[[OpenNIC|OpenNIC]]的DNS服务器也支持.bit域名。

== 废弃 ==
2019年7月，OpenNIC投票决定放弃.bit命名空间，理由是“支持NameCoin域名存在许多问题”以及多个项目之间的冲突。表决通过。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Should OpenNIC drop support for NameCoin [OpenNIC Wiki]|url=https://wiki.opennic.org/votings/drop_namecoin|access-date=2021-01-23|website=wiki.opennic.org}}</ref>Namecoin开发者杰里米·兰德（Jeremy Rand）对这一举动表示欢迎，感谢OpenNIC并将其描述为“正确的决定”。<ref>{{Cite web|title=OpenNIC does the right thing: listens to security concerns and shuts down its centralized Namecoin inproxy|url=https://www.namecoin.org/2019/07/30/opennic-does-right-thing-shuts-down-centralized-inproxy.html|website=namecoin.org}}</ref><ref name="ZDNet France 2019">{{cite web | title=Namecoin : l’intégrité, mais à quel prix? | website=ZDNet France | date=2019-08-01 | url=https://www.zdnet.fr/actualites/namecoin-l-integrite-mais-a-quel-prix-39888667.htm | language=fr | access-date=2021-11-27}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=What is Namecoin's relationship to OpenNIC?|url=https://www.namecoin.org/docs/faq/#what-is-namecoins-relationship-to-opennic|website=namecoin.org}}</ref>

